data.description: Interested in reducing your closing costs or buying down the interest rate? $5,000 SELLER ASSIST available now! to this well maintained end unit townhome in Birchwood. This floor plan offers 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. From the front entry you will be great with lots of natural lighting from the oversized window. The main floor has an open living room and dining room, eat in kitchen, main bedroom with a walk-in closet, full bathroom and a laundry/ utility area. Upstairs you will find 3 more spacious bedrooms and a hallway bathroom. Outside the home the new owners will enjoy a large carport with storage shed and entryway with privacy fencing. In the rear of the home is a fenced in backyard with 2 sliding glass doors inside. The current owner's have made made many improvements to the house including replacement siding, windows, and a new HVAC in 2019. The home owners association fee includes trash removal twice a week, landscaping outside of the fence and snow removal. Located adjacent to Lodal Creek Park with playground, ball courts and picnic area. Convenient location with easy access to Limerick and Collegeville shopping, dining and major routes.
